channel.title: Account Rollback
channel.description:
Less than 24 hours ago, I decided to give botting a try. I left it on all night and made 400k and 62 Woodcutting by chopping Oaks.
I've been cutting Yews all morning, and put the laptop on the floor and left it whilst I was watching telly, glanced back to find I was logged out.
So I log back in and find that I'm level 20 Woodcutting! No messages in my inbox, bank still has 400k and no ban.
So do I continue to bot or am I in for it now?

Most of you; saying “KEEP BOTTING” Are pretty dumb. JaGeX roll’ed him back because they thought he was botting, so they watch the account. If that very same day/2days he gets his Woodcutting back to 65, they WILL ban you. If he kept not botting for say about a week, they would give his stats back. This is not a lie. They’re doing this to potential botters; to see if they are acctually botting.
